quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,55,""
  26,56,""
  26,57,"So, We expelled them from gardens and springs,"
  27,28,""
  27,29,"She said: "
  27,30,""
  28,1,"Tâ-Sîn-Mîm"
  28,2,"These are the Verses of the manifest Book (that makes clear truth from falsehood, good from evil)."
  28,3,"We recite to you some of the news of Mûsâ (Moses) and Fir‘aun (Pharaoh) in truth, for a people who believe (in this Qur’ân, and in the Oneness of Allâh)."